metadata.description:
"Blessings of the All-Dick" is treasured by both art scholars and lay observers alike. 

Thick strokes and bold loads gracefully capture the tangible result of the Big Bust, as all things are cast into creation. The central figure glows with the omnipresent grace of the All-Dick.

Circa early-Refractory Period, artist unknown
metadata.name: Blessings of the All-Dick
